---
title: "supportsInterface (WorkflowRouter)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_parent: super.supportsInterface(interfaceId)
    q_check_parent --> q_return_true: parent returns true
    q_check_parent --> q_check_receiver: parent returns false
    q_check_receiver --> q_return_true: interfaceId == type(IReceiver).interfaceId
    q_check_receiver --> q_return_false: no match
    q_return_true --> [*]: return true
    q_return_false --> [*]: return false

    note right of q_check_receiver
        INV-001: supports IReceiver interface in addition to PausableWithAccessControl interfaces
    end note
